hiveArticle.title: B&W Photo Contest - Water - Entry #1 - River Kaveri
hiveArticle.body:
This is my first entry for the B&W photo contest initiated by @daveks and sponsored by @papa-pepper.

### River Kaveri in Coorg, India

River Kaveri is on of the holy rivers in India. It originates from Madikeri district in Karnataka. This image was taken near Abbey Falls.

<hr>

 ![image](https://img.esteem.ws/e2oxrv8ncw.jpg)

<hr>

Camera : Nokia 6, Edited to Black and White
